casebody.data:
Yvette M. CORMIER, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
PF FITNESS-MIDLAND, LLC, Defendant-Appellee,
and
Pla-Fit Franchise, LLC, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Planet Fitness Holdings, LLC, Planet Fitness Equipment, LLC, Planet Fitness NAF, LLC, PFIP, LLC, and TSG Consumer Partners, LLC, Defendants. SC: 158372
COA: 331286 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 2, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 26, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
